The cinematographic studies have been through transformations because the information and communication technological progress This paper is to analyze some changes in the cinema in terms of the audiovisual diversification. However, to try to join the cinema with the territory of the audiovisual demands a series of theoretical accommodations In the first part of this article, the point of view from denomination is discussed. Secondly, the text expose the subject of this expanded cinema, analyzing both its connection with the communication system and its exchange of dimension for to inscribe the discussion about this subject in a theoretical register scientifically supported.